                <section class="box normal">
                    <h2><i class="icon-group"></i> Organizer</h2>
                    <h3>Who runs F!rosh Week?</h3>
                    <p>
                        F!rosh Week is run by the Orientation Committee, a division of the University of Toronto
                        Engineering Society, the student government body of the Faculty of Applied Science and
                        Engineering.
                    </p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
